name: GG EZ
tagline: The code used for the GG EZ application
body:
# Welcome to Summoner's Rift!

## All of the Champs!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- View all of the champions in the game.
- Up-to-date with new champ releases.
- See their abilities and their stats.

![Main Menu](http://i.imgur.com/YHoWXM7.png)


## Bragging Rights!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Enter your summoner name to see your summoner stats.
- See your Ranked stats.
- See your recent matches complete with builds and match type.

![Summoner Data](http://i.imgur.com/BGoi8NJ.png)


## More Feature Coming Soon!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- iPad Version & Apple Watch Support
- In-Depth Game Stats
- Share Games to Facebook

[iOS]( https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gg-ez/id1014052962?ls=1&mt=8)

For any features you would like to see added or just general feedback please contact:
contactggezsupp@gmail.com
